The goal is to show that the composition f ≫ g = 0 in Rep ℤ G. This means for all x : Additive 𝒪[L]ˣ, (v L) ((ker_v L) x) = 0. We can use ker_v_ker which says Function.Exact (ker_v L) (v L), meaning ∀ y, y ∈ Set.range (ker_v L) ↔ (v L) y = 0. For any x, (ker_v L) x is in the range of ker_v L, so (v L) ((ker_v L) x) = 0.

For the proof: use ext to reduce to checking pointwise, then apply the exactness condition.
-/
